### 通知系统API测试

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api/v1

### 0. 准备测试数据

### 0.1 注册测试用户1
# @name notifyUser1
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "notify_user_001",
  "password": "123456",
  "nickname": "通知测试用户1",
  "email": "notify001@campus.com",
  "phone": "13800000021",
  "schoolId": 1,
  "role": "student"
}

### 0.2 注册测试用户2
# @name notifyUser2
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

