### ==================== 1. 发送通知（管理员功能） ====================

### 1.1 管理员发送系统通知给指定用户
# @name sendToUser
POST {{baseUrl}}/notification/send
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "userId": 1,
  "title": "系统维护通知",
  "content": "系统将于今晚22:00-23:00进行维护升级，届时将暂停服务，请提前做好准备。",
  "notifyType": "system",
  "relatedType": null,
  "relatedId": null
}

### 1.2 管理员发送回答通知
# @name sendAnswerNotify
POST {{baseUrl}}/notification/send
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "userId": 1,
  "title": "你的问题有新回答",
  "content": "用户「通知测试用户2」回答了你的问题「如何学习Spring Boot」",
  "notifyType": "answer",
  "relatedType": "question",
  "relatedId": 1
}

### 1.3 管理员发送任务通知
# @name sendTaskNotify
POST {{baseUrl}}/notification/send
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "userId": 2,
  "title": "新任务分配",
  "content": "你被分配了新任务「完成图书馆志愿服务」，请在本周五前完成。",
  "notifyType": "task",
  "relatedType": "task",
  "relatedId": 1
}

### 1.4 管理员发送活动通知
# @name sendActivityNotify
POST {{baseUrl}}/notification/send
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "userId": 1,
  "title": "活动即将开始",
  "content": "你报名的活动「校园马拉松」将于明天上午8:00开始，请准时参加。",
  "notifyType": "activity",
  "relatedType": "activity",
  "relatedId": 1
}

### 1.5 管理员发送私信通知
# @name sendMessageNotify
POST {{baseUrl}}/notification/send
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "userId": 2,
  "title": "你收到了新私信",
  "content": "用户「通知测试用户1」给你发送了私信",
  "notifyType": "message",
  "relatedType": "message",
  "relatedId": 1
}

### 1.6 管理员发送举报处理通知
# @name sendReportNotify
POST {{baseUrl}}/notification/send
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "userId": 1,
  "title": "举报处理结果",
  "content": "你举报的内容已经处理完毕，感谢你对平台的监督。",
  "notifyType": "report",
  "relatedType": "report",
  "relatedId": 1
}

### 1.7 管理员发送社团通知
# @name sendClubNotify
POST {{baseUrl}}/notification/send
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "userId": 3,
  "title": "社团活动通知",
  "content": "计算机协会将于本周六举行技术分享会，欢迎参加。",
  "notifyType": "club",
  "relatedType": "club",
  "relatedId": 1
}

### 1.8 管理员发送通知给所有用户（群发）
# @name sendToAll
POST {{baseUrl}}/notification/send
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "userId": null,
  "title": "平台公告",
  "content": "欢迎使用CampusLink平台！我们致力于为高校师生提供便捷的资源互助与问答服务。",
  "notifyType": "system",
  "relatedType": null,
  "relatedId": null
}

### 1.9 非管理员尝试发送通知（应该失败）
# @name unauthorizedSend
POST {{baseUrl}}/notification/send
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token3}}

{
  "userId": 2,
  "title": "测试通知",
  "content": "这是一条测试通知",
  "notifyType": "system",
  "relatedType": null,
  "relatedId": null
}

### ==================== 2. 获取通知列表 ====================

### 2.1 获取我的所有通知（第一页）
# @name getMyNotifications
GET {{baseUrl}}/notification/my?page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token1}}

### 2.2 获取我的所有通知（第二页）
# @name getMyNotificationsPage2
GET {{baseUrl}}/notification/my?page=2&pageSize=5
Authorization: Bearer {{token1}}

### 2.3 获取我的所有通知（默认分页参数）
# @name getMyNotificationsDefault
GET {{baseUrl}}/notification/my
Authorization: Bearer {{token2}}

### 2.4 用户2获取通知列表
# @name getUser2Notifications
GET {{baseUrl}}/notification/my?page=1&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token2}}

### 2.5 用户3获取通知列表
# @name getUser3Notifications
GET {{baseUrl}}/notification/my
Authorization: Bearer {{token3}}

### ==================== 3. 获取未读通知 ====================

### 3.1 获取我的未读通知列表
# @name getUnreadNotifications
GET {{baseUrl}}/notification/unread?page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token1}}

### 3.2 获取未读通知（第二页）
# @name getUnreadPage2
GET {{baseUrl}}/notification/unread?page=2&pageSize=5
Authorization: Bearer {{token1}}

### 3.3 用户2获取未读通知
# @name getUser2Unread
GET {{baseUrl}}/notification/unread
Authorization: Bearer {{token2}}

### 3.4 用户3获取未读通知
# @name getUser3Unread
GET {{baseUrl}}/notification/unread
Authorization: Bearer {{token3}}

### ==================== 4. 获取未读通知数量 ====================

### 4.1 用户1获取未读通知数量
# @name getUnreadCount1
GET {{baseUrl}}/notification/unread-count
Authorization: Bearer {{token1}}

### 4.2 用户2获取未读通知数量
# @name getUnreadCount2
GET {{baseUrl}}/notification/unread-count
Authorization: Bearer {{token2}}

### 4.3 用户3获取未读通知数量
# @name getUnreadCount3
GET {{baseUrl}}/notification/unread-count
Authorization: Bearer {{token3}}

### ==================== 5. 标记通知为已读 ====================

### 5.1 标记指定通知为已读（通知ID需要从上面的查询中获取,请先执行步骤2.1获取通知列表）
# @name markAsRead
# 注意：请将下面的1替换为从步骤2.1查询结果中获取的实际notificationId
PUT {{baseUrl}}/notification/1/read
Authorization: Bearer {{token1}}

### 5.2 标记另一条通知为已读
# @name markAsRead2
# 注意：请将下面的2替换为从步骤2.1查询结果中获取的实际notificationId
PUT {{baseUrl}}/notification/25/read
Authorization: Bearer {{token1}}

### 5.3 用户2标记通知为已读
# @name markAsRead3
PUT {{baseUrl}}/notification/3/read
Authorization: Bearer {{token2}}

### 5.4 尝试标记不属于自己的通知（应该失败）
# @name unauthorizedRead
PUT {{baseUrl}}/notification/1/read
Authorization: Bearer {{token2}}

### 5.5 标记不存在的通知（应该失败）
# @name markNonexistent
PUT {{baseUrl}}/notification/99999/read
Authorization: Bearer {{token1}}

### ==================== 6. 标记所有通知为已读 ====================

### 6.1 用户1标记所有通知为已读
# @name markAllAsRead1
PUT {{baseUrl}}/notification/read-all
Authorization: Bearer {{token1}}

### 6.2 用户2标记所有通知为已读
# @name markAllAsRead2
PUT {{baseUrl}}/notification/read-all
Authorization: Bearer {{token2}}

### 6.3 用户3标记所有通知为已读
# @name markAllAsRead3
PUT {{baseUrl}}/notification/read-all
Authorization: Bearer {{token3}}

### 6.4 标记所有为已读后再次查询未读数量（应该为0）
# @name checkUnreadAfterMarkAll
GET {{baseUrl}}/notification/unread-count
Authorization: Bearer {{token1}}

### ==================== 7. 删除通知 ====================

### 7.1 删除指定通知
# @name deleteNotification
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/notification/25
Authorization: Bearer {{token1}}

### 7.2 删除另一条通知
# @name deleteNotification2
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/notification/2
Authorization: Bearer {{token1}}

### 7.3 用户2删除通知
# @name deleteNotification3
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/notification/3
Authorization: Bearer {{token2}}

### 7.4 尝试删除不属于自己的通知（应该失败）
# @name unauthorizedDelete
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/notification/4
Authorization: Bearer {{token2}}

### 7.5 删除不存在的通知（应该失败）
# @name deleteNonexistent
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/notification/99999
Authorization: Bearer {{token1}}

### 7.6 删除后查询通知列表（验证删除成功）
# @name checkAfterDelete
GET {{baseUrl}}/notification/my
Authorization: Bearer {{token1}}

### ==================== 8. 清空已读通知 ====================

### 8.1 用户1清空所有已读通知
# @name clearRead1
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/notification/clear-read
Authorization: Bearer {{token1}}

### 8.2 用户2清空所有已读通知
# @name clearRead2
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/notification/clear-read
Authorization: Bearer {{token2}}

### 8.3 用户3清空所有已读通知
# @name clearRead3
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/notification/clear-read
Authorization: Bearer {{token3}}

### 8.4 清空后查询通知列表（只剩未读通知）
# @name checkAfterClear
GET {{baseUrl}}/notification/my
Authorization: Bearer {{token1}}

### ==================== 9. 综合测试场景 ====================

### 9.1 发送通知 -> 查询未读 -> 标记已读 -> 再次查询
# Step 1: 发送通知
# @name scenario1Step1
POST {{baseUrl}}/notification/send
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "userId": 1,
  "title": "综合测试通知",
  "content": "这是一条用于测试的通知",
  "notifyType": "system",
  "relatedType": null,
  "relatedId": null
}

### 9.2 Step 2: 查询未读通知数量
# @name scenario1Step2
GET {{baseUrl}}/notification/unread-count
Authorization: Bearer {{token1}}

### 9.3 Step 3: 获取未读通知列表
# @name scenario1Step3
GET {{baseUrl}}/notification/unread
Authorization: Bearer {{token1}}

### 9.4 Step 4: 标记所有为已读
# @name scenario1Step4
PUT {{baseUrl}}/notification/read-all
Authorization: Bearer {{token1}}

### 9.5 Step 5: 再次查询未读数量（应该为0）
# @name scenario1Step5
GET {{baseUrl}}/notification/unread-count
Authorization: Bearer {{token1}}

### 9.6 Step 6: 清空已读通知
# @name scenario1Step6
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/notification/clear-read
Authorization: Bearer {{token1}}

### 9.7 Step 7: 查询所有通知（应该为空或很少）
# @name scenario1Step7
GET {{baseUrl}}/notification/my
Authorization: Bearer {{token1}}

